            <title>[HBASE-3135] Make our MR jobs implement Tool and use ToolRunner so can do -D trickery, etc.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3135</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Our TIF can take a bunch of config.  If our MR jobs &amp;#8211; rowcounter, export, import, etc. &amp;#8211; all implemented Tool/ToolRunner, then we&apos;d pick up the Tool cmdline parse of -D that sets config.  Small change.  Lots of utility.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
